{"tid":1441860,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"唔該大家真係要對準返政權","createTime":"2019-08-10T18:18:52.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-11T02:25:45.000Z","uid":244599,"like":90,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":39,"replies":[{"pid":"040fbd57687aa0f8a461cbaa91a5b7bfc3011439","tid":1441860,"uid":244599,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T18:18:52.000Z","msg":"我知又有又會話我分化撚<br />\n<br />\n但我想講而家連日嘅示威活動 其實好多時都只係不停屌警犬 圍警局<br />\n 已經好耐冇啲對政府有直接影響同指名性嘅運動<br />\n 我都知偏地開花固然重要 但係呢幾日我都聽到身邊啲淺黃親戚開始話我地將警察變成磨心 所以真係好應該要再做嗰三步曲<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">遊行-&gt;死線-&gt;升級</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: violet;\">要求政府回應先有用</span></span><br />\n如果唔係我地真係會輸<br />\n每日淨係識係到笑尻班警犬 打飛機係冇用<br />\n記住<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">五大訴求</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">對準政權</span></span>"},{"pid":"13da508912be61d23ec630ccab33d5c991f42b2c","tid":1441860,"uid":244599,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T18:19:23.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"2896829a239349ebe43d39f45f6835bc6be8066c","tid":1441860,"uid":244599,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T18:19:33.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"55b9d53015145e5f7f1167dec9338546ae3a72b4","tid":1441860,"uid":244599,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T18:19:43.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"8710bc6f992862f7876cd90f6437010bb44a28b5","tid":1441860,"uid":244599,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T18:19:54.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"38d200ed9b7ef3ac29aaf1f28aa443aa1f7a2c39","tid":1441860,"uid":109820,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T18:20:03.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n<br />\n【小心中計】如果我係敵人，我會想<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1441838\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1441838</a>"},{"pid":"212479efee2df046499ab57f6a8a48fd7a9ec037","tid":1441860,"u